-- Venezuela takes over local Stanford bank: source
-- 
-- Thu Feb 19, 2009 6:59am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/02/19/us-stanford-venezuela-bank-idUSTRE51I2GK20090219

 

 CARACAS  (Reuters) - Venezuela took control of a local bank owned by Allen Stanford, who faces U.S. fraud charges, a government source said on Thursday as the impact of the American case spread through Latin America. 

 (Reporting by Ana Isabel Martinez, Writing by Saul Hudson, Editing by Brian Ellsworth and  Sandra Maler )